[ANNOUNCER 2] Next,
a greeting from our director.

00:13:19.292 --> 00:13:20.417
[STUDENTS cheering]

00:13:20.458 --> 00:13:21.542
[BOY] Incredible!

00:13:21.583 --> 00:13:23.917
[IRUMA]
As in, the king of the demons?

00:13:23.958 --> 00:13:25.375
-DIRECTOR [singsongy]: Iruma!
-Huh?

00:13:25.417 --> 00:13:27.083
It's me, your loving Grandpa!

00:13:27.125 --> 00:13:28.583
[IRUMA] He's the director?!

00:13:28.625 --> 00:13:29.583
-[muffled gasp]
-[BOY] Iruma?

00:13:29.625 --> 00:13:31.250
[GIRL] The director's grandkid?

00:13:31.292 --> 00:13:33.125
[SULLIVAN] Yes, indeed.

00:13:33.167 --> 00:13:35.167
My grandson now
attends this school.

00:13:35.208 --> 00:13:36.875
And he's so precious
and adorable,

00:13:36.917 --> 00:13:38.875
I could squeeze him
till his eyes pop out.

00:13:38.917 --> 00:13:41.375
[IRUMA] Oh, no,
please don't embarrass me!

00:13:41.417 --> 00:13:44.500
And right here I have the photo
we took just a bit ago.

00:13:45.542 --> 00:13:47.000
Look, it's me and my grandson.

00:13:47.042 --> 00:13:48.625
[IRUMA] He blew my cover!

00:13:48.667 --> 00:13:50.500
-[GIRL 1] That's him?
-[GIRL 2] His grandson Iruma?

00:13:50.542 --> 00:13:52.792
Copies will be made available
for everyone later.

00:13:52.833 --> 00:13:54.875
[IRUMA]
I promise, nobody wants that.

00:13:54.917 --> 00:13:57.750
Well, that's really
all I wanted to say, so...

00:13:57.792 --> 00:13:58.833
Bye!

00:13:59.917 --> 00:14:01.375
And now, we'll have a greeting

00:14:01.417 --> 00:14:03.125
from the
new students' representative.

00:14:03.167 --> 00:14:05.000
[BOY] Isn't that the guy
who scored the highest

00:14:05.042 --> 00:14:06.583
on the entrance exam?

00:14:06.625 --> 00:14:09.625
[ANNOUNCER 2] The representative
of the new students, Asmodeus.

00:14:09.667 --> 00:14:11.250
What a hottie.

00:14:11.292 --> 00:14:12.542
So that's what he looks like.

00:14:12.583 --> 00:14:13.875
Ooh, curse me, please.

00:14:13.917 --> 00:14:15.417
Yeah, he's alright.

00:14:15.458 --> 00:14:17.042
-[sighs]
-[ANNOUNCER 2] What? Sorry?

00:14:17.083 --> 00:14:18.417
[IRUMA]
He's a perfect distraction.

00:14:18.458 --> 00:14:20.375
[ANNOUNCER 2] Giving the address
in his place is

00:14:20.417 --> 00:14:23.125
our honor student, young Iruma.

00:14:23.167 --> 00:14:24.083
[IRUMA] Why?!

00:14:24.125 --> 00:14:25.375
[GIRL 1] Huh? What the heck?

00:14:25.417 --> 00:14:26.917
-[murmuring]
-[GIRL 2] This guy's doing it?

00:14:26.958 --> 00:14:27.958
[SULLIVAN giggling]

00:14:28.000 --> 00:14:30.417
[IRUMA] I knew it, I'm finished!

00:14:30.458 --> 00:14:32.542
[ANNOUNCER 2]
Iruma, please come to the stage.

00:14:32.583 --> 00:14:33.417
[whimpers]

00:14:33.458 --> 00:14:36.042
Oh, wow, he's just a baby.

00:14:37.042 --> 00:14:39.042
[STUDENTS murmuring]

00:14:40.542 --> 00:14:43.042
[whimpering in fear]

00:14:43.083 --> 00:14:44.083
[BOY 1] Check it out.

00:14:44.125 --> 00:14:45.375
He's in front
of a crowd this big

00:14:45.417 --> 00:14:46.500
and not even blinking.

00:14:46.542 --> 00:14:47.833
[BOY 2] That kid's got guts.

00:14:47.875 --> 00:14:48.833
[IRUMA] I can't breathe

00:14:48.875 --> 00:14:50.542
when I'm on the spot like this.

00:14:50.583 --> 00:14:52.542
If you wouldn't mind
giving your greeting.

00:14:52.583 --> 00:14:54.250
[IRUMA] Seriously?

00:14:54.292 --> 00:14:56.917
What am I even
supposed to say here?

00:14:56.958 --> 00:14:58.125
[gasps]

00:15:00.458 --> 00:15:02.250
[SULLIVAN] I've sent you
these words of wisdom

00:15:02.292 --> 00:15:03.792
for good luck and well wishes,

00:15:03.833 --> 00:15:05.208
so that you won't trip and fall

00:15:05.250 --> 00:15:06.875
throughout your upcoming
school days.

00:15:06.917 --> 00:15:08.458
Your loving Grandpa.

00:15:08.500 --> 00:15:11.833
[IRUMA] Huh? I'm just
supposed to read this out loud?

00:15:11.875 --> 00:15:12.917
[grunts]

00:15:12.958 --> 00:15:14.917
Guess I have no choice.

00:15:14.958 --> 00:15:16.542
[inhales deeply]

00:15:16.583 --> 00:15:18.208
Aberuhauke.

00:15:18.250 --> 00:15:19.792
[ALL gasp]

00:15:19.833 --> 00:15:21.708
♪

00:15:21.750 --> 00:15:23.417
[ALL gasp]

00:15:23.458 --> 00:15:24.708
[murmuring]

00:15:24.750 --> 00:15:26.958
Tarutoudari. Iusabebe.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:29.083
[ALL gasp]

00:15:30.500 --> 00:15:33.458
[murmuring]

00:15:34.750 --> 00:15:36.458
[gasps]

00:15:36.500 --> 00:15:39.000
[IRUMA] Why's everyone so quiet?

00:15:39.042 --> 00:15:41.125
Risutouru. Aburuze.

00:15:41.167 --> 00:15:42.250
Sutoumanu.

00:15:42.292 --> 00:15:43.875
[screaming in disbelief]

00:15:43.917 --> 00:15:45.292
Aberuge.

00:15:45.333 --> 00:15:47.583
[screaming continues]

00:15:47.625 --> 00:15:48.667
Uru.

00:15:51.792 --> 00:15:52.875
Mahoraba.

00:15:52.917 --> 00:15:55.625
♪

00:15:55.667 --> 00:15:57.250
Tsurezaza.

00:16:05.375 --> 00:16:06.667
-[ALL cheering]
-[GIRL 1] No way!

00:16:06.708 --> 00:16:08.292
-[BOY 1] Holy crap!
-[GIRL 2] Seriously?

00:16:08.333 --> 00:16:09.917
-[BOY 2] He did it!
-[GIRL 3] He said all of it!

00:16:09.958 --> 00:16:10.958
-[BOY 3] What the hell?
-Huh?

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:12.333
-Hey, you.
-[gasps]

00:16:12.375 --> 00:16:14.750
You can't go chanting
forbidden spells like that.

00:16:14.792 --> 00:16:16.000
Um, what?

00:16:16.042 --> 00:16:17.875
They're taboo,
and for good reason.

00:16:17.917 --> 00:16:19.500
If you were to stutter
or read it wrong,

00:16:19.542 --> 00:16:20.917
your body could've exploded.

00:16:20.958 --> 00:16:22.000
That's just common sense.

00:16:22.042 --> 00:16:23.125
[IRUMA] News to me!

00:16:23.167 --> 00:16:24.875
[gasps] How could I know

00:16:24.917 --> 00:16:26.125
it was so dangerous?

00:16:26.167 --> 00:16:28.917
That stunt was foolish,
reckless and crazy.

00:16:28.958 --> 00:16:31.000
And unbelievably awesome, too.

00:16:31.042 --> 00:16:32.333
[gasps sharply]

00:16:32.375 --> 00:16:34.500
Only a total idiot
would use that spell.

00:16:34.542 --> 00:16:37.708
Or an oblivious demon
who doesn't fear death.

00:16:37.750 --> 00:16:40.958
Uh, by the way, sir,
what exactly does that spell do?

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:42.250
If it works, it'll prevent you

00:16:42.292 --> 00:16:44.000
from tripping and falling
the whole day.

00:16:44.042 --> 00:16:45.125
Wait, that's it?

00:16:54.375 --> 00:16:57.250
You may call me Asmodeus Alice.

00:16:57.292 --> 00:16:59.250
Uh... hi, there.

00:16:59.292 --> 00:17:01.458
♪

00:17:01.500 --> 00:17:04.708
Why do I suddenly feel like
I'm about to die?

00:17:04.750 --> 00:17:06.458
[BOY] The head of the class
and the honor student

00:17:06.500 --> 00:17:08.167
are about to duke it out.

00:17:08.208 --> 00:17:09.208
[GIRL] This should be great.

00:17:10.417 --> 00:17:12.083
[whimpers] Excuse me,

00:17:12.125 --> 00:17:14.125
but are you gonna eat me?

00:17:14.167 --> 00:17:17.708
[ASMODEUS] I was supposed
to deliver the school greeting.

00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:20.583
The punishment for thieving
that spotlight from me

00:17:20.625 --> 00:17:22.542
is most assuredly death.

00:17:22.583 --> 00:17:24.042
[NARRATOR] Asmodeus Alice.

00:17:24.083 --> 00:17:27.417
A demon well-known
for his mastery of fire spells.

00:17:27.458 --> 00:17:28.875
[gasps]

00:17:28.917 --> 00:17:32.042
And since you
so rudely stole my thunder,

00:17:32.083 --> 00:17:33.833
I reserve the right
to test your mettle

00:17:33.875 --> 00:17:36.500
and see if you're
truly worthy of it.

00:17:36.542 --> 00:17:37.667
Agreed?

00:17:37.708 --> 00:17:39.125
[cheering]

00:17:39.167 --> 00:17:41.167
Wow, they're really into this.

00:17:41.208 --> 00:17:43.708
Now, you only have mere moments

00:17:43.750 --> 00:17:45.208
to try and prove to me that you

00:17:45.250 --> 00:17:48.958
are superior to me
with your body!

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:50.208
♪

00:17:50.250 --> 00:17:51.708
[cheering]

00:17:51.750 --> 00:17:53.708
[battle cry]

00:17:53.750 --> 00:17:55.917
♪

00:17:55.958 --> 00:17:58.042
[BOY 1] Asmodeus is so badass.

00:17:58.083 --> 00:18:00.792
No other newbie could handle
fireballs like that.

00:18:00.833 --> 00:18:02.208
[BOY 2] He's amazing, but...

00:18:02.250 --> 00:18:04.375
[BOY 3]
Yeah. He hasn't hit him once.

00:18:04.417 --> 00:18:05.667
[screams]

00:18:05.708 --> 00:18:07.667
Hey, wait.
Please, sir, calm down.

00:18:07.708 --> 00:18:08.958
[yelps]

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:11.875
♪

00:18:11.917 --> 00:18:12.875
Now, take this!

00:18:12.917 --> 00:18:14.875
[screaming]

00:18:14.917 --> 00:18:17.208
♪

00:18:17.250 --> 00:18:19.458
[screaming continues]

00:18:19.500 --> 00:18:20.958
[ASMODEUS] Why can't I hit him?

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:24.917
♪

00:18:24.958 --> 00:18:29.167
[BOTH panting]

00:18:30.417 --> 00:18:32.125
[NARRATOR]
For 20 straight minutes,

00:18:32.167 --> 00:18:34.917
Iruma managed
to dodge every single attack.

00:18:34.958 --> 00:18:38.208
What the hell?
I haven't hit you once.

00:18:38.250 --> 00:18:40.417
I know. Sorry about that.

00:18:40.458 --> 00:18:42.792
[NARRATOR] How was such
a feat remotely possible?

00:18:42.833 --> 00:18:46.292
In truth, it's because
he's unfortunate.

00:18:46.333 --> 00:18:47.792
After being
put through endless hell

00:18:47.833 --> 00:18:49.292
by his garbage parents,

00:18:49.333 --> 00:18:52.250
by default, he became
a master of avoiding anything.

00:18:52.292 --> 00:18:54.958
Whether dangerous,
scary, or painful,

00:18:55.000 --> 00:18:56.333
he dodged it all.

00:18:56.375 --> 00:18:57.542
[IRUMA] Now's my chance.

00:18:57.583 --> 00:18:59.583
I need to apologize.

00:18:59.625 --> 00:19:01.000
[NARRATOR]
He may have zero offense,

00:19:01.042 --> 00:19:02.958
but his defense is infinite.

00:19:03.000 --> 00:19:05.542
[NARRATOR] If given a name,
this rare power would be called

00:19:05.583 --> 00:19:08.625
"Overwhelming Crisis
Evasion Capability."

00:19:08.667 --> 00:19:10.500
Uh, for real, I'm sorry.

00:19:10.542 --> 00:19:12.625
-[BOY 1] Iruma's a beast.
-Huh?

00:19:12.667 --> 00:19:15.125
[BOY 2] He hasn't even
tried to attack him yet.

00:19:15.167 --> 00:19:17.458
[BOY 3] Wait. Is he saying
he's not worth his time?

00:19:17.500 --> 00:19:18.625
Whoa!

00:19:18.667 --> 00:19:19.500
[gasps]

00:19:19.542 --> 00:19:21.000
Well, are they right?

00:19:21.042 --> 00:19:23.917
Am I so not worth attacking
you won't even bother?

00:19:23.958 --> 00:19:25.375
No, no, no, no, no, no, no!

00:19:25.417 --> 00:19:27.833
It's not you at all.
I'm the unworthy bug here.

00:19:27.875 --> 00:19:29.625
-[jeering]
-[whistles]

00:19:29.667 --> 00:19:31.875
[BOY 1] That means
you're less than a bug.

00:19:31.917 --> 00:19:33.250
[BOY 2] Run home to your mommy,

00:19:33.292 --> 00:19:34.375
you coward.

00:19:34.417 --> 00:19:36.042
[BOY 3] Yeah! You tell him.

00:19:36.083 --> 00:19:37.500
[IRUMA] You've got it all wrong!

00:19:38.542 --> 00:19:39.958
I will not abide this.

00:19:41.708 --> 00:19:43.083
If magic won't work,

00:19:43.125 --> 00:19:46.292
I'll just have to take you down
using martial arts.

00:19:46.333 --> 00:19:48.083
Prepare for destruction!

00:19:48.125 --> 00:19:50.167
[yelps, screams]

00:19:50.208 --> 00:19:52.333
[NARRATOR] He uses his
opponent's strength to parry.

00:19:52.375 --> 00:19:55.417
Another part of his Overwhelming
Crisis Evasion Capability.

00:19:55.458 --> 00:19:57.417
-[ASMODEUS yelling]
-[GIRL screams] Eiko!

00:19:57.458 --> 00:19:59.167
[gasps] Careful, watch out!

00:19:59.208 --> 00:20:00.417
[grunts]

00:20:00.458 --> 00:20:01.375
We'll fall!

00:20:02.458 --> 00:20:03.667
[BOTH gasp]

00:20:06.542 --> 00:20:07.833
[DALI]
If it works, it'll prevent you

00:20:07.875 --> 00:20:09.667
from tripping and falling
the whole day.

00:20:09.708 --> 00:20:11.500
What's going on here?

00:20:11.542 --> 00:20:13.333
A duel on
the first day of school?

00:20:13.375 --> 00:20:15.458
That's never happened before.

00:20:15.500 --> 00:20:16.708
[NARRATOR]
Those who witnessed the duel

00:20:16.750 --> 00:20:18.167
that day would later say...

00:20:18.208 --> 00:20:19.917
[indistinct chatter]

00:20:21.458 --> 00:20:24.708
"Yes, it was,
without exaggeration.

00:20:24.750 --> 00:20:28.167
A perfectly executed
German suplex."

00:20:28.208 --> 00:20:30.958
[cheering]

00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:33.958
[IRUMA] I'm doomed.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:37.083
♪

00:20:37.125 --> 00:20:38.458
[BOY 1]
"Chanting a forbidden spell

00:20:38.500 --> 00:20:40.125
at the entrance ceremony."

00:20:40.167 --> 00:20:42.333
"Gave the head of the class
a concussion."

00:20:42.375 --> 00:20:44.083
"Behold,
the thoroughbred honor student

00:20:44.125 --> 00:20:46.458
Iruma's amazing attack."

00:20:46.500 --> 00:20:48.833
[BOY 2]
That honor student's insane!

00:20:48.875 --> 00:20:50.958
[GIRL] I heard he once
saved a girl's life.

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:53.208
[SULLIVAN] I'd expect
nothing less from my grandson.

00:20:53.250 --> 00:20:55.292
You have such
a bright future ahead.

00:20:55.333 --> 00:20:58.500
No, I don't. What I did
was completely awful.

00:20:58.542 --> 00:20:59.458
I gotta apol--

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:01.958
[gasps sharply]

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:07.458
Oh. hey, Asmodeus.

00:21:09.208 --> 00:21:10.458
[groans]

00:21:11.958 --> 00:21:12.833
Huh?

00:21:12.875 --> 00:21:15.500
♪

00:21:15.542 --> 00:21:18.000
I am now at your service, Iruma.

00:21:18.042 --> 00:21:19.000
Huh?

00:21:19.042 --> 00:21:20.750
There's nothing more to say.

00:21:20.792 --> 00:21:24.125
I squarely, handily
lost to you in our earlier duel.

00:21:24.167 --> 00:21:26.750
On top of that, I was informed
that you carried me

00:21:26.792 --> 00:21:28.542
all the way to the infirmary.

00:21:28.583 --> 00:21:30.708
And I, Asmodeus, was moved

00:21:30.750 --> 00:21:33.417
far beyond what mere words
could even express.

00:21:33.458 --> 00:21:35.000
Huh? But wait, I...

00:21:35.042 --> 00:21:37.708
Written Demon law dictates
that the defeated party

00:21:37.750 --> 00:21:39.167
must serve the victor.

00:21:39.208 --> 00:21:40.458
Therefore...

00:21:41.500 --> 00:21:42.500
[gasps]

00:21:44.917 --> 00:21:46.792
...I pledge
my staunch fealty to you,

00:21:46.833 --> 00:21:49.500
and will aide you in ruling
over this school forever.

00:21:49.542 --> 00:21:51.625
What?! Wait a minute, hang on!

00:21:51.667 --> 00:21:53.000
First, you need servants,

00:21:53.042 --> 00:21:55.417
so that's going to be
the entire student body.

00:21:55.458 --> 00:21:56.667
[screams]

00:21:56.708 --> 00:21:58.333
Now, who shall I slay first?

00:21:58.375 --> 00:22:00.417
Your wish is my command.

00:22:00.458 --> 00:22:02.083
[SULLIVAN] Oh, grandson.

00:22:02.125 --> 00:22:04.792
Can I make this the main picture
on the school's website?

00:22:04.833 --> 00:22:06.625
[IRUMA] I wish you wouldn't.

00:22:06.667 --> 00:22:08.792
[NARRATOR]
Iruma Suzuki, age 14,

00:22:08.833 --> 00:22:10.917
enrolled at
the demon school Babyls,

00:22:10.958 --> 00:22:13.292
has now acquired
one subordinate.

00:22:13.333 --> 00:22:14.917
[IRUMA cries]

00:23:45.917 --> 00:23:48.542
Su... ki... ma.

00:23:48.583 --> 00:23:51.583
Master, please ask me
to do anything.

00:23:51.625 --> 00:23:54.375
Sure. But I don't need
anything right now, thank you.

00:23:54.417 --> 00:23:57.208
Iruma saved me
from certain death.

00:23:57.250 --> 00:24:00.417
I wanna thank him,
and maybe get closer to him.

00:24:00.458 --> 00:24:01.708
-Irum--
-[growls]

00:24:01.750 --> 00:24:03.917
Uh, what was that?
Something wrong?

00:24:03.958 --> 00:24:05.708
I felt
a sinister presence nearby.

00:24:05.750 --> 00:24:08.708
Scary. Oh, my gosh,
he's so scary.

00:24:08.750 --> 00:24:09.875
[NARRATOR]
Can she get close enough

00:24:09.917 --> 00:24:11.292
to Iruma to thank him?

00:24:11.333 --> 00:24:13.042
You can do it, Eiko.

00:24:15.500 --> 00:24:17.375
[IRUMA] I never dreamed
I'd become a demon's grandson

00:24:17.417 --> 00:24:18.792
and go to a demon school.

00:24:18.833 --> 00:24:22.458
Uh, Asmodeus?
Please, don't bow so low.

00:24:22.500 --> 00:24:24.667
I don't need a piggyback ride.
I can walk.

00:24:24.708 --> 00:24:27.333
Carry me instead?
That's not any better.

00:24:27.375 --> 00:24:29.292
I don't need to ride
on your shoulders, either.

00:24:29.333 --> 00:24:30.542
Put me down!

00:24:30.583 --> 00:24:33.208
Next on "Welcome to
Demon School Iruma-kun,"

00:24:33.250 --> 00:24:34.875
"Familiars Summoned."

00:24:34.917 --> 00:24:36.208
Wait. I'm human, though.

00:24:36.250 --> 00:24:38.917
I can't summon anything. Help!

00:24:38.958 --> 00:24:41.000
♪

